Answer
Why?

Suppose the user asks

How is MATLAB related to Turbine Engineering?

At this point the LLM knows nothing.

If you call the LLM immediately, it has no graph context.

Instead, the retriever first collects:

Turbine Engineering
        │
      within
        ▼
HotEnd Design
        │
      includes
        ▼
Blade Design
        │
       uses
        ▼
MATLAB

Now we have useful evidence.

Then Cell 17 builds the context

It converts the graph into readable text.

Example

Retrieved Knowledge Graph

1.
Turbine Engineering is within HotEnd Design.

2.
HotEnd Design includes Blade Design.

3.
Blade Design uses MATLAB.
Now comes the Prompt

Only here.

